---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
import { site } from '../data/site';

const title = site.title;
const description = site.description;
---
<MainLayout title={title} description={description} pathname="/">
  <section class="bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_top,#fed7aa,transparent_45%),linear-gradient(180deg,#fff7ed_0%,#fafaf9_65%)]">
    <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-6xl gap-12 px-6 py-20 lg:grid-cols-[1.1fr_0.9fr] lg:items-center">
      <div>
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-orange-600">Kitchen gifts, Glendora style</p>
        <h1 class="mt-4 max-w-3xl text-5xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-stone-900 sm:text-6xl">
          A warmer way to discover dinnerware, cookware, and thoughtful gifts.
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-6 max-w-2xl text-lg leading-8 text-stone-700">
          Kitchen Supplies 4 Less pairs practical value with Kathy's personal curation, spotlighting elegant bone china,
          enamel dutch ovens, and gift-ready pieces for celebrations, hosting, and everyday cooking.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-4">
          <a href="https://www.kitchensupplies4less.com/" class="rounded-full bg-orange-500 px-6 py-3 font-semibold text-white hover:bg-orange-600">Shop the store</a>
          <a href="/blog/mothers-day-kitchen-gifts-2026" class="rounded-full border border-stone-300 px-6 py-3 font-semibold text-stone-800 hover:border-orange-500 hover:text-orange-600">Read the gift guide</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-[2rem] border border-orange-100 bg-white p-8 shadow-[0_30px_80px_-40px_rgba(120,53,15,0.35)]">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-stone-500">Why this angle works</p>
        <ul class="mt-6 space-y-4 text-sm leading-7 text-stone-700">
          <li><strong>Local trust:</strong> Glendora-centered messaging turns a generic catalog into a recognizable local brand story.</li>
          <li><strong>Gift intent:</strong> The strongest search openings are bone china, kitchen gifts, and Mother's Day buying moments.</li>
          <li><strong>Curated feel:</strong> Featured picks avoid the endless-scroll problem shoppers get on big-box marketplaces.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-16">
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 md:flex-row md:items-end md:justify-between">
      <div>
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-orange-600">Featured categories</p>
        <h2 class="mt-2 text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Built around the products with the clearest story.</h2>
      </div>
      <p class="max-w-2xl text-sm leading-7 text-stone-600">
        The site architecture follows the strongest positioning from TKJ-325, leading with affordable elegance, useful cookware,
        and gift-focused local search terms rather than trying to outrank Amazon on generic catalog pages.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-10 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">
      {site.featuredProducts.map((product) => (
        <article class="rounded-[1.75rem] border border-stone-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-orange-600">{product.category}</p>
          <h3 class="mt-3 text-2xl font-semibold text-stone-900">{product.name}</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-7 text-stone-600">{product.description}</p>
          <p class="mt-4 text-sm font-medium text-stone-800">{product.benefit}</p>
          <div class="mt-6 flex items-center justify-between">
            <span class="text-lg font-semibold text-stone-900">${product.price}</span>
            <a href={`/products/${product.slug}`} class="font-semibold text-orange-600 hover:text-orange-700">View page</a>
          </div>
        </article>
      ))}
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="border-y border-stone-200 bg-white">
    <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-6xl gap-8 px-6 py-16 lg:grid-cols-3">
      <div class="rounded-[1.5rem] bg-stone-100 p-6">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-stone-500">Story</p>
        <h3 class="mt-3 text-2xl font-semibold">Kathy's curation gives the site a human center.</h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-7 text-stone-600">This isn't a faceless kitchen catalog. It's a Glendora-rooted selection shaped around gifting, hosting, and practical everyday cooking.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-[1.5rem] bg-stone-100 p-6">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-stone-500">SEO</p>
        <h3 class="mt-3 text-2xl font-semibold">Schema, canonicals, sitemap, and clean crawl controls are built in.</h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-7 text-stone-600">Each page includes metadata tuned for local and seasonal kitchen-shopping intent, with structured data matched to the page type.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-[1.5rem] bg-stone-100 p-6">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-stone-500">CTA</p>
        <h3 class="mt-3 text-2xl font-semibold">Every featured page pushes traffic back to the main store.</h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-7 text-stone-600">The goal is not to replace the existing storefront. It is to create a focused acquisition layer that channels visitors into kitchensupplies4less.com.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>
